{"tid":1506744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸同胞wangzhenhao支持香港人打警察 大家快啲入黎瘋狂多謝佢支持港人抗爭","createTime":"2019-08-26T01:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T03:35:26.000Z","uid":21262,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f122aafc7190718df2dad254eb2dae01309e8910","tid":1506744,"uid":21262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:52:26.000Z","msg":"保護手足我就遮遮佢名先 <br />\n<br />\n呢位企係正義之師呢邊既大陸人叫王震？定王震浩？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">IG ac:wangzhenhao12321 </span></span><br />\n第三張相唔知係咪佢架車個車牌呢？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沪KC7051 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n見佢冇啦啦鬧手足收錢又鬧人地呀媽做雞 之後忽然轉軚支持香港人抗爭 唔知係咪忽然開竅呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點樣PM之前打到帝吧班五毛一仆一碌既手足 幫佢將呢個事蹟發揚光大呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DUgx5uB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDUgx5uB.jpg&h=5e737417&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Onxk2X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Onxk2X.png&h=ae86ae9a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jyMViPD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjyMViPD.png&h=87189cba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aeffc0becc5e9f087b8991f31b0a65c4dd7ecb3a","tid":1506744,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:52:38.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogleDrive: 91機場文宣資源 (手足有新貨話我知，會Upload上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxjBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=152591be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/op